  <brief_title>Low Dose Spinal Morphine for Post-video-assisted Thoracoscopic Surgery</brief_title>
  <official_title>Low Dose Spinal Morphine for Post-video-assisted Thoracoscopic Surgery. A Pilot Study</official_title>
  <sponsors>
